{
 "name": "RPlog_Sensing_Orson",
 "title": "Sensing Orson",
 "summary": "Hiding in Plaxton City under the assumed name Annalise, the fugitive fallen Jedi (formerly Jessalyn Valios) and her ebony-skinned Selas companion Shale grow uneasy as they sense the approach of someone she dreads -- Orson, the man whose hold over her she fears. Rattled from recent run-ins with the Corellian Kyyel, Annalise reflects on her unknown parentage and the dark anger hardening within her, declaring she is no longer afraid and resolving to slip offworld past the starport and past Orson by any means. Shale, blunt and paranoid in the staring crowds, admits he almost hopes Orson will try to stop them, hinting he would finish what he started aboard the Dimlyn Titan, and warns her the city crawls with liars and thieves. As the formidable Horansi K'tyyri saunters past, Shale departs alone to scout the spaceport ahead, leaving Annalise steeling herself for the confrontation she never wanted.",
